'''大马士革之战'''（'''The Battle of Damascus'''，或 '''Operation Damascus Volcano'''）开始于2012年7月15日，是[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]的一部分。一些报道称有数千名反对派武装围攻首都[[大马士革|大马士革]]，而反对派则把针对大马士革发起的战役称为代号为“大马士革火山与叙利亚地震”（Damascus volcano and Syrian earthquake）的解放行动。

在此期间大马士革的大部分商店都闭门停业，路上的交通车辆也很少。有不少居民已经逃离该地。

==战斗==
===反对派进攻===
;7月15日
其中一支反對派武裝从[[杜马_(叙利亚)|杜马]]朝首都进发。激烈战斗发生在一些市区，政府軍想把反對派赶出去。战斗导致通往[[机场|机场]]的道路被关闭<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/jul/16/syria-fighting-damascus-live?CMP=twt_gu |title=Guardian live updates |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2012-07-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120716094748/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/jul/16/syria-fighting-damascus-live?CMP=twt_gu |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

;7月16日
在南部的Midan与Tadhamon地区发生了激烈交火<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-18859453 |title=Syria unrest: Second day of fierce Damascus clashes |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2012-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120718074917/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-18859453 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，敘軍尽力想使用坦克与装甲车包围反對派。自由军控制了这两个地区，而敘軍想夺回它们<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.skynews.com.au/topstories/article.aspx?id=772508 |title=Damascus fighting a 'turning point' |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2020-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116181426/https://www.skynews.com.au/topstories/article.aspx?id=772508 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。根据叙国家电视台报道，政府軍在战斗中打死了超过80名反对派士兵<ref name=clashescontinue>{{cite web|url=http://www.globaltimes.cn/content/721521.shtml|title=Syrian capital's clashes continue in southern part|publisher=|accessdate=25 October 2014|archive-date=2013-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130728161937/http://www.globaltimes.cn/content/721521.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

;7月17日
在叙利亚中央银行所在的Sabaa Bahrat广场附近发生了交火，这个广场曾举办过几次支持政府的大型集会活动<ref name=centraldamascus>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-18866265 |title=Syria conflict: Central Damascus hit by clashes |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2012-07-17 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120717135625/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-18866265 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在叙议会大厦附近也有交战<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/story/2012/07/17/syria-damascus-fighting.html |title=Damascus sees heavy fighting, activists say |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2012-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120820051753/http://www.cbc.ca/news/world/story/2012/07/17/syria-damascus-fighting.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在南部的Midan与Kfar Sousa地区以及北部的Barzeh与Qabun地区战斗仍在持续中。政府軍对这些地区使用火炮攻击，尤其是针对Midan地区。同时，在Barzeh与Qabun地区有武装直升机从空中袭击反对派<ref name=centraldamascus/>。后来，在以上四个地区都有武装直升机参与攻击<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rferl.org/content/syria-damascus-fighting-escalates-defections-continue/24647884.html |title=Syrian Regime Uses Attack Helicopters In Damascus; Defections Continue |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2016-08-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160821193013/http://www.rferl.org/content/syria-damascus-fighting-escalates-defections-continue/24647884.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[SANA|SANA]]报道，反对派已经从Nahr Aisha地区撤退到了Midan地区继续战斗<ref name=clashesspread>{{cite web|url=http://www.kcautv.com/story/19047105/clashes-spread-to-new-areas-in-syrian-capital|title=Siouxland church creates buzz surrounding bees found in sanctuary|author=Bria Bell|work=SIOUXLANDMATTERS}}{{Dead link}}</ref>。从[[戈兰高地|戈兰高地]]转移回来的部队正在防御首都<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/jul/17/syria-crisis-damascus-clashes-live#block-20 |title=3.20pm: Syria |accessdate=2012-07-19 |archive-date=2012-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121115194254/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/jul/17/syria-crisis-damascus-clashes-live#block-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

反对派宣布他们在16日打死了超过70名政府軍与親政府民兵<ref name=fightingrages>{{cite web|url=http://thestar.com.my/news/story.asp?file=/2012/7/17/worldupdates/2012-07-17T131724Z_35_BRE8640R3_RTROPTT_0_UK-SYRIA-CRISIS&sec=Worldupdates|title=Syria fighting rages in capital, Russia pressed|publisher=|accessdate=2014-10-25|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://archive.today/20121220031959/http://thestar.com.my/news/story.asp?file=/2012/7/17/worldupdates/2012-07-17T131724Z_35_BRE8640R3_RTROPTT_0_UK-SYRIA-CRISIS&sec=Worldupdates|archivedate=2012-12-20}}</ref>，敘政府称摧毁了14辆反对派的车辆<ref name="soldiersjump"/>，一名敘軍军官称他们在Qaboun地区的战斗中打死了33名、打伤15名、以及俘虏145名反对派<ref name=liberate>{{Cite web |url=http://news.kuwaittimes.net/2012/07/17/syrian-rebels-battling-to-liberate-damascus/ |title=-{Syrian rebels battling to ‘liberate’ Damascus}- |accessdate=2012-07-19 |archive-date=2013-01-12 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130112100323/http://news.kuwaittimes.net/2012/07/17/syrian-rebels-battling-to-liberate-damascus/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。活动家Shakeeb al-Jabri称总计超过200名政府軍士兵已被打死打伤。亲政府的网站报道，一名副警察局长、-{准}-将Issa Duba因伤死亡<ref name=guardian2>{{cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/jul/17/syria-crisis-damascus-clashes-live#block-8|title=11.09am: Syria|author=Matthew Weaver|work=the Guardian|accessdate=2014-10-25|location=London|date=2012-07-17|archive-date=2012-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121115194254/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/jul/17/syria-crisis-damascus-clashes-live#block-8|dead-url=no}}</ref>。自由军称他们摧毁了一辆、俘获了一辆装甲车，里面的政府軍士兵也被消灭<ref name=losesgrip>{{cite news|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/assad-loses-grip-on-damascus-as-rebels-begin-to-close-in-on-regime-7946872.html|title=Assad loses grip on Damascus as rebels begin to close in on regime|work=The Independent|accessdate=2014-10-25|location=London|first=Loveday|last=Morris|date=2012-07-17|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019125201/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/middle-east/assad-loses-grip-on-damascus-as-rebels-begin-to-close-in-on-regime-7946872.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=guardian1>{{cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/jul/17/syria-crisis-damascus-clashes-live#block-22|title=4.23pm: Syria|author=Matthew Weaver|work=the Guardian|accessdate=2014-10-25|location=London|date=2012-07-17|archive-date=2012-11-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121115194254/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/jul/17/syria-crisis-damascus-clashes-live#block-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>。反对派也称在Qaboun地区击落了一架直升机<ref name=converge>{{cite web|url=http://www.firstpost.com/world/syrian-rebels-converge-on-capital-russia-pressed-380992.html|title=Syrian rebels converge on capital, Russia pressed|author=FP Staff|date=2012-07-17|work=Firstpost|accessdate=2012-07-19|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019093932/http://www.firstpost.com/world/syrian-rebels-converge-on-capital-russia-pressed-380992.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=centraldamascus/>。

一名自由军军官宣布解放大马士革的战役已经开始<ref name=centraldamascus/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lbcgroup.tv/news/41304/iraq-calls-on-citizens-in-syria-to-return-home |title=FSA: 'Battle for liberation' of Damascus has begun |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2015-09-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150910223551/http://www.lbcgroup.tv/news/41304/iraq-calls-on-citizens-in-syria-to-return-home |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不过反对派发言人But Tarek称，目前在大马士革发生的还只是小规模冲突，他说真正的解放战斗还没到来<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/jul/17/syria-crisis-damascus-clashes-live#block-14 |title=1.44pm: Syria |accessdate=2012-07-19 |archive-date=2012-11-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121115194254/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/2012/jul/17/syria-crisis-damascus-clashes-live#block-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。敘利亞信息部长Omran Zoabi表示，政府軍包围并击退了反对派，其余的还在战斗中<ref name=converge/>。

;7月18日
{{main|2012年7月大马士革炸弹袭击事件}}

在夜晚，当地居民说在离总统府100米的地方有交火发生。[[SANA|SANA]]报道政府軍进入了Midan地区；SOHR报道直升机在空袭Barzeh与Qaboun地区<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/news/world/syrian-defense-minister-dawoud-rajha-killed-suicide-blast-senior-officials-wounded-article-1.1116739 |title=Syrian defense minister Dawoud Rajha killed in suicide blast, other senior officials wounded |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2017-12-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171206192231/http://www.nydailynews.com/news/world/syrian-defense-minister-dawoud-rajha-killed-suicide-blast-senior-officials-wounded-article-1.1116739 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在Kfar Souseh与Nahr Aisha地区也有交火<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/syria-rebels-government-forces-battle-in-damascus/1/208855.html |title=Syrian rebels, government forces battle in Damascus |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019094523/http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/syria-rebels-government-forces-battle-in-damascus/1/208855.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在空袭之后，自由军宣布从Midan地区撤退。[[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]]报道敘軍轰炸了该地。傍晚，Midan地区被敘軍控制。自由军则转移至al-Sabina地区<ref name=nowlebanon>{{cite web|url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=253828|title=NOW Lebanon - NOW Syria 18.7.2012|archiveurl=https://archive.is/20120906140521/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=253828|archivedate=2012-09-06|deadurl=yes|accessdate=2012-07-23}}</ref>。

反对派宣布，敘軍军官Mohammad al-Bardan率领他的士兵们变节加入了反对派<ref name=nowlebanon/>。[[Al_Arabiya|Al Arabiya]]报道，这些士兵来自第三装甲師<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4257524,00.html |title=Celebrations, defections follow Damascus blast |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025191358/http://www.ynetnews.com/articles/0,7340,L-4257524,00.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。不过，没有其他新闻报道给予证实。路透社报道，敘軍从一处俯瞰首都的高山上轰炸一些郊区<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.todayszaman.com/newsDetail_getNewsById.action?newsId=286976 |title=Syrian army artillery hit Damascus from mountain |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2012-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120718235123/http://www.todayszaman.com/newsDetail_getNewsById.action?newsId=286976 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。[[Al_Jazeera|Al Jazeera]]同时报道，自由军击落两架正在空袭塔達蒙（Tadamon）与Al-Hajjar al-Aswad地区的直升机<ref name=nowlebanon/>。SOHR报道，60名政府軍士兵在第三、第四天被打死<ref name="D">{{Cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/07/20127189355415804.html |title=Damascus blast 'kills' top Assad officials |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2012-07-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120718202720/http://www.aljazeera.com//news/middleeast/2012/07/20127189355415804.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

=== 政府軍反攻 ===
7月19日，政府軍發動攻勢，試圖驅逐已進入大馬士革的反對派部隊。<ref name=freshoffensive>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-18897773|title=Syria conflict: Fresh offensive against rebels|work=BBC News|accessdate=25 October 2014|date=19 July 2012|archive-date=2020-11-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201116133530/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-18897773|dead-url=no}}</ref>

7月20日，敘軍在当天结束時已完全控制市中心和市中心以外地区，尽管一些外围地区仍有交火发生。在[[雅爾矛克難民營|雅爾矛克難民營]]附近戰鬥的反對派部隊也被政府軍和親政府的巴勒斯坦人派系擊敗。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2012/jul/20/syria-crisis-rebels-seize-borders-live#block-34|title=4.27pm|author=Matthew Weaver|work=the Guardian|accessdate=25 October 2014|location=London|date=20 July 2012|archive-date=2013-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130513225639/http://www.guardian.co.uk/world/middle-east-live/2012/jul/20/syria-crisis-rebels-seize-borders-live#block-34|dead-url=no}}</ref>

7月21日，[[法新社|法新社]]报道敘軍在20日已经控制了塔達蒙（Tadamon）、Qaboun、Barzeh以及Midan地区。而在Jobar、Kfar Sousa与Mazeeh地区，战斗仍在持续。後來證實反对派仍控制着Barzeh地区<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thejakartaglobe.com/afp/syrian-forces-launch-all-out-damascus-assault/531828 |title=Syrian forces launch all-out Damascus assault {{!}} The Jakarta Globe<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2012-12-09 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20121209104610/http://www.thejakartaglobe.com/afp/syrian-forces-launch-all-out-damascus-assault/531828 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。活动家称战斗发生在北部的Barzeh与Rukneddine地区。一名活动家说一个位于Khaled bin Waleed大街的警察局受到袭击，而反对派正在首都进行[[游击战|游击战]]<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/07/2012720142235155363.html |title=Syria strikes back at rebels in Damascus |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2019-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190908194832/https://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/07/2012720142235155363.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。早晨，当地居民表示处于平静状态。SOHR报道，敘軍在轰炸Al-Kaddam与Assali郊区，Al-Hajar Al-Aswad与塔達蒙地区的居民也说战斗在持续着<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=421278 |title=Lebanon news - NOW Lebanon -Clashes in Syria's Aleppo, tense calm in Damascus<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2012-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120724094518/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=421278 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

上载网络的视频显示，北部的al-Tal郊区，警察部队向一些自由军投降<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-18937514 |title=Syria crisis: Heavy clashes in second city of Aleppo |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121134520/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-18937514 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，当天有12个平民死亡，其中7人是被狙击手射杀的<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/2/8/48346/World/Region/At-least--killed-in-Syria-Saturday-Rights-group.aspx |title=At least 90 killed in Syria Saturday: Rights group |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2020-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113003707/http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/2/8/48346/World/Region/At-least--killed-in-Syria-Saturday-Rights-group.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

身為基督徒的Nabil Zougheib[[准将|-{准}-将]]和他的妻子、儿子在家里被暗杀<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052702303644004577524653025270434.html |title=Syrian Conflict Draws In Christians |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2013-06-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130608013150/http://online.wsj.com/article/SB10001424052702303644004577524653025270434.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

7月22日，当地居民说发生了猛烈的炮轰。活动家说直升机朝南部郊区发射火箭炮<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/07/22/227667.html |title=Fierce fighting in Damascus, Ban Ki-Moon sending peacekeeping chief to Syria |access-date=2014-10-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141025181546/http://english.alarabiya.net/articles/2012/07/22/227667.html |archive-date=2014-10-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。一个记者报道直升机也在空袭Barzeh地区<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.aljazeera.com/topic/syria/damascus-neighbourhood-shelled-helicopter-gunships |title=Damascus neighbourhood shelled by 'helicopter gunships'. |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304055646/http://blogs.aljazeera.com/topic/syria/damascus-neighbourhood-shelled-helicopter-gunships |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

第四装甲師袭击了Barzeh地区<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=421469&MID=149&PID=2 |title=Lebanon news - NOW Lebanon -Feared forces launch new assault on Damascus<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2012-07-24 |archive-url=https://wayback.archive-it.org/all/20120724131844/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArchiveDetails.aspx?ID=421469 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/07/22/us-syria-crisis-fighting-idUSBRE86L03F20120722 |title=Syria government forces, rebels battle in Damascus, Aleppo {{!}} Reuters<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924165550/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/07/22/us-syria-crisis-fighting-idUSBRE86L03F20120722 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该部队也攻击了Mezzeh地区<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.lbcgroup.tv/news/42084/protesters-damage-hafez-assads-statue-shelling-res |title=LBCI News {{!}} Damascus heavily shelled as Turkey deploys missiles on Syria border<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2015-06-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150607214258/http://www.lbcgroup.tv/news/42084/protesters-damage-hafez-assads-statue-shelling-res |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.rt.com/news/syria-helicopters-bomb-damascus-780/ |title=Govt helicopters bombing Damascus districts not confirmed — RT<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2017-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019095934/https://www.rt.com/news/syria-helicopters-bomb-damascus-780/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，大约1000名政府軍在装甲车、坦克和[[推土机|推土机]]的支援下进入了该地<ref name="retakescontrol">{{Cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/9418993/Syria-Assad-regime-retakes-control-of-Damascus-suburbs.html |title=Syria: Assad regime retakes control of Damascus suburbs |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2012-08-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120825190749/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/9418993/Syria-Assad-regime-retakes-control-of-Damascus-suburbs.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。政府軍迫使反对派从Rukn al-Din地区撤退<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-18943316 |title=BBC News - Syria crisis: Fresh clashes rock Damascus and Aleppo<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2020-11-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201129062107/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-18943316 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。国家媒体报道，政府軍正在消灭残余的反对派<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/07/22/us-syria-crisis-idUSBRE8610SH20120722 |title=Syrian forces bombard Damascus, fight rages in Aleppo {{!}} Reuters<!-- Bot generated title --> |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924165552/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/07/22/us-syria-crisis-idUSBRE8610SH20120722 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。活动家说，当天Barzeh地区也被敘軍控制，有至少5个年轻的反对派士兵被集体处决<ref name="retakescontrol"/><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.aljazeera.com/topic/syria/syrian-army-forces-overrun-northern-damascus-district-barzeh-and-summarily-execute-five |title=Syrian Army Forces overrun northern Damascus district of Barzeh and summarily execute five young men |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304052821/http://blogs.aljazeera.com/topic/syria/syrian-army-forces-overrun-northern-damascus-district-barzeh-and-summarily-execute-five |dead-url=no }}</ref>。反对派首次针对大马士革的攻势目前看来已经结束<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/9418601/Syrian-troops-driving-rebels-out-of-Damascus-strongholds.html |title=Syrian troops driving rebels out of Damascus strongholds |accessdate=2012-07-23 |archive-date=2020-11-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201113065405/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/worldnews/middleeast/syria/9418601/Syrian-troops-driving-rebels-out-of-Damascus-strongholds.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。活动家报道说政府軍在Mezzeh地区处决了至少20名非武装的人士，因为他们被怀疑帮助了反对派<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/07/201272275230449605.html |title=Syria army launches fierce attacks on rebels |accessdate=2012-07-29 |archive-date=2012-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120830192058/http://www.aljazeera.com/news/middleeast/2012/07/201272275230449605.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

叙国家电视台播出了一些其他阿拉伯国家的士兵死于Qaboun地区的画面，包括2名[[埃及|埃及]]人与3名[[约旦|约旦]]人<ref>[http://208.43.232.81/eng/337/2012/07/24/432866.htm Syrian TV Shows Bodies of Terrorists of Arab Nationalities Killed by the Syrian Army in al-Qaboun Neighborhood]{{dead link|date=十一月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>。

=== 反對派敗退 ===
7月23日，敘政府宣布攻擊首都的反对派大多已被击败<ref name="suffers">{{Cite web |url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/07/23/syria-conflict-damascus_n_1695623.html |title=Syria Conflict: Damascus Suffers Destruction, Hunger As Fighting Hits Country's Heart |accessdate=2012-07-29 |archive-date=2016-03-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160307034312/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/2012/07/23/syria-conflict-damascus_n_1695623.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在Mezze与Barzeh地区发现了23具被处决的尸体，一些人身上有明显的酷刑印记<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.aljazeera.com/topic/syria/least-23-summarily-executed-sunday |title=At least 23 "summarily executed" on Sunday |accessdate=2012-07-29 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304112757/http://blogs.aljazeera.com/topic/syria/least-23-summarily-executed-sunday |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

7月24日，在[[德拉雅|德拉雅]]郊区发现了24具被处决的反对派尸体。南部的哈賈爾阿斯瓦德（Hajar al-Aswad）地区受到了一些炮击<ref name=rebelpush>{{Cite web |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/07/24/us-syria-crisis-idUSBRE8610SH20120724 |title=Syrian forces battle rebel push on central Aleppo |accessdate=2012-07-29 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924165626/http://www.reuters.com/article/2012/07/24/us-syria-crisis-idUSBRE8610SH20120724 |dead-url=no }}</ref>，反对派报道政府軍攻击了Qaddam与al-Aswad地区<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=422199 |title=Syria army attacks Damascus rebel districts, activists say |accessdate=2012-07-29 |archive-date=2013-01-04 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20130104043657/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=422199 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。记者Alex Thompson描述称政府軍在首都获得了全面胜利，士兵在卡车上欢庆他们的胜利<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://blogs.channel4.com/alex-thomsons-view/assads-ironfist-defence-syrian-capital/2401 |title=Assad's 'iron-fist defence' of Syrian capital |accessdate=2012-07-29 |archive-date=2014-10-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141026012000/http://blogs.channel4.com/alex-thomsons-view/assads-ironfist-defence-syrian-capital/2401 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。晚上，活动家报道说，反对派大多已经撤离了首都<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.newsday.com/news/world/top-general-friend-of-syrian-president-defects-1.3856655 |title=Top general, friend of Syrian president, defects |accessdate=2012-07-29 |archive-date=2012-07-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120728055219/http://www.newsday.com/news/world/top-general-friend-of-syrian-president-defects-1.3856655 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

7月25日，大馬士革市郊被反對派控制的城鎮Al-Tal遭到敘軍猛烈炮轟。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.aljazeera.com/topic/syria/syrian-forces-have-reportedly-fired-artillery-and-rocket-barrages-rebel-held-damascus|title=Syrian forces have reportedly fired artillery and rocket barrages at rebel-held Damascus suburb of al-Tal|work=Al Jazeera Blogs|accessdate=25 October 2014|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065231/http://blogs.aljazeera.com/topic/syria/syrian-forces-have-reportedly-fired-artillery-and-rocket-barrages-rebel-held-damascus|dead-url=no}}</ref>

7月26日，反對派在大馬士革僅餘的控制區其中之一哈賈爾阿斯瓦德區據報發生了戰鬥。[[雅爾矛克難民營|雅爾矛克難民營]]據報也有戰鬥發生。<ref>{{Cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/world/2012/jul/26/syrian-forces-gather-aleppo-assault |title=Syrian forces gather for Aleppo assault |publisher=The Guardian |date=2012-07-26 |accessdate=2016-08-30 |archive-date=2017-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171207205006/https://www.theguardian.com/world/2012/jul/26/syrian-forces-gather-aleppo-assault |dead-url=no }}</ref>

7月29日，SANA稱政府軍已肅清哈賈爾阿斯瓦德區的反對派部隊。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.farsnews.com/newstext.php?nn=9104251905 |title=Syrian Army Disbands Tens of Terrorist Cells in Damascus |accessdate=2016-08-30 |archive-date=2012-08-13 |archive-url=https://swap.stanford.edu/20120813042105/http%3A//english.farsnews.com/newstext.php?nn%3D9104251905 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>

反對派在大馬士革的殘餘部隊在塔達蒙區集結。敘軍於8月1日開始進攻該區。8月2日，附近的雅爾矛克難民營被炮彈擊中，造成15至21人喪生。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-19106250|title=Syria crisis: Fighting rages ahead of UN Assembly vote|work=BBC News|accessdate=25 October 2014|date=3 August 2012|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123224155/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/world-middle-east-19106250|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>[http://www.wctrib.com/event/article/id/96446/group/homepage/ In Syria, mortars kill 21 in Damascus refugee camp]{{dead link|date=十一月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2012/aug/3/syria-mortars-kill-21-damascus-refugee-camp/|title=Mortars kill at least 20 in Damascus refugee camp|work=The Washingtion Times|accessdate=25 October 2014|archive-date=2017-10-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171019093933/http://www.washingtontimes.com/news/2012/aug/3/syria-mortars-kill-21-damascus-refugee-camp/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

8月4日，塔達蒙區的武裝分子被肅清，領導進攻行動的一名將領宣稱整個大馬士革已經由敘利亞軍隊完全控制。<ref name=general>{{cite web|url=http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=425065|title=All of Damascus now under army control, general says|date=4 August 2012|publisher=|accessdate=25 October 2014|archive-url=https://archive.today/20130104063812/http://www.nowlebanon.com/NewsArticleDetails.aspx?ID=425065|archive-date=2013-01-04|dead-url=yes}}</ref>敘軍稱塔達蒙區有800名反對派武裝分子，當中300人在最後進攻中被殲滅。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.aljazeera.com/topic/syria/syrian-army-declares-al-tadamun-damascus-district-free-insurgency|title=Syrian army declares Al Tadamun in Damascus district as 'free of insurgency'|work=Al Jazeera|date=5 August 2012|accessdate=26 September 2012|archive-date=2015-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151014100900/http://blogs.aljazeera.com/topic/syria/syrian-army-declares-al-tadamun-damascus-district-free-insurgency|dead-url=no}}</ref>

